description: This common Sakura purrs with a rating of 64, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 64, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, 3 for East, Box for South, and 5 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [64 Votes, Common]
